<p>The 5th edition of "Strategies for Theory Construction in Nursing" by Jacqueline Fawcett and Eileen DeSanto-Madeya is available in both print and electronic formats. You can find it through online retailers such as Amazon, Barnes &amp; Noble, and Google Books.</p>
